title: Riot Explain this
body: Look at the Screenshot above (sorry for the bad quality)

replies.body: It looks like you *might* be referring to the mastery scores, which really shouldn't be compared since you're playing different champions in different lanes/roles. Am I on the right track here?
looks like bot was inting once again
You're CS is also too low for a higher score in a 38 minute game. Notice how Yi got an S- and has 44 more CS than you and he was only JG.
Also the fact that they never bought any control wards probably didn't help.
Should have gone for more assists than just hogging all of the kills ;)
